1.    No Abusing
We're all in this together to create a welcoming environment. Let's treat everyone with respect. Healthy debates are natural, but kindness is required.

2.    No Racism/Bullying
Make sure everyone feels safe. Bullying of any kind isn't allowed, and degrading comments about things such as race, religion, culture, sexual orientation, gender or identity will not be tolerated.

3.    Respectful Conduct
Don’t talk down other Gangs in recruitment channels. Give everyone a fair chance to recruit numbers. Keep it friendly when speaking in #⏩general

4.    Self Promoting YouTube/Twitch/Groups
Give more to this group than you take. Self-promotion is allowed, however spam is not. Do not post constantly, promoting yourself. This can be done in #:file_cabinet:community-content.

5.    Respect Others Privacy
Being part of this group requires mutual trust. Authentic, expressive discussions make groups great, but may also be sensitive and private. What's shared in the group should stay in the group.

6.    Advertising Servers
Any advertisement of Servers must be agreed before being posted with the Group Owner.

7.    Bot Presence
Do not invite unapproved bots/selfbots. Inviting unapproved bots will result in punishment. 

8.    Multiple Accounts
Multiple discord accounts are not permitted, if you require multiple discord accounts please speak to an admin who can advise on the issue. 
